**New Listing** Sunday Open House 2-5PM
 Altadena 
4 Bed | 4 Bath ( Message me for more Details )

The unparalleled privacy of this home offers tranquility unlike any other. Situated at the end of a private drive w/ over a half acre of professionally designed grounds, the home boasts an ambiance perfect for living & entertaining. A glistening pool & surrounding water features provide ample serenity to escape to. One is met w/ welcoming architecture upon entering, featuring open beam high ceilings & skylights. Large Chefs kitchen provides not just the necessities, but also a gorgeous view into the backyard space & mountains. The layout of this home creates a wonderful space, utilizing every inch functionally & aesthetically. The 3 car garage, grilling space w/ dining & seating areas, multiple balconies w/ views off the bedrooms, marble bath w/ spa tub & separate shower are just some of the extra features provided. The approachable sophistication is inviting, the elegance of the details makes visitors want to linger, & the connection between the architecture & landscape is romantic.
